h4. Actor:
Administrator.

h4. Description:
Name of use case represent its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Settings|guide:_ShowApplicationPlugin] option from top menu bar.
* "Settings" sub menu of left menu should show as default.
* Click *Inventory Item* link.
* Show List of *Inventory Item* in [Landing Page|guide:ShowItemCategoryInventoryActionService].

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "List Inventory Item" privilege.

h4. Process:
* Get list of *Inventory Item* from server (default: 15 at Max).
* Following columns should show in grid view:
** Serial
** ID (Default: Invisible)
** Name
** Code
** Unit
** Item Type
** Valuation Type
** Finished Product

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** *Inventory Item* will be listed in grid view.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

